顺利，小学初中时我不知道自己想要什么，高中时压力太大几乎退学，大学时我又因为自己的问题无法毕业。\n但是在工作后我反而逐渐建立起了自信心，就像是突然进入了康庄大道。</p>\n<p>最近我又经历了许多，受到了一些启发，因此决定写下这篇文章，既是记录我的过去，也同时思考下未来的路该怎么走。</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://thiscute.world/posts/a-quarter-of-the-way-through-life/\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://thiscute.world/posts/a-quarter-of-the-way-through-life/</a></p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/966753","replies":31,"created_ts":1692476152,"created":"04:15:52","title":"两岸猿声啼不住，轻舟已过万重山——我的四分之一人生","author":"ryan4yin","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/ryan4yin","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/2362ce7bdf2845a92240cc2f6609e001?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":966760,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1650095340","description":"<p>V 友们，大家好，你有配置家庭服务器吗？会跑一些什么应用呢？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/966760","replies":25,"created_ts":1692492062,"created":"08:41:02","title":"你有配置家庭服务器吗？会跑一些什么应用呢？","author":"stephen2009","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/stephen2009","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/0215c0ea2122f92a233abfc3291985b5?s=24&d=retro"}]